title: Taylor Swift’s Easter Eggs Have Gone Out of Control (Extended) | The Tonight Show
author: The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon
description:
Taylor Swift shares how her cryptic Easter eggs originated and how they transformed into a rabbit hole, confirms the "All Too Well" video is full of them and hints at which songs she might perform on Saturday Night Live.
